  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19) and prisons
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This page provides guidance for families and friends of those in prison in England and Wales during the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

  </div>
